~eOSMOSE emulator default keys~0
Up Arrow    - Pad1 UP 
Down Arrow  - Pad1 DOWN 
Left Arrow  - Pad1 LEFT left arrow
Right Arrow - Pad1 RIGHT right arrow
Z           - Pad1 Button A
X           - Pad1 Button B
P           - PAUSE/SELECT 
S           - START (GameGear) 
Ctrl-R      - Reset Game
Ctrl-F      - Toggle fullscreen
Ctrl-M      - Toggle menubar
